    area: 'Turkish',
    instructions: { en: 'Heat oven to 200C/180C fan/gas 6. Toss the sweet potato chunks with the olive oil and some seasoning, and spread on a baking parchment-lined baking sheet. Roast for 30 - 35 mins until tender and golden. Cool at room temperature.\n\nWhen just about cool whisk together all the dressing ingredients with a little more seasoning and gently toss through the potato chunks – use your hands to avoid breaking them up.', ro: 'Heat oven to 200C/180C fan/gas 6. Amesteca usor the sweet potato chunks with the olive oil and some seasoning, and spread on a baking parchment-lined baking sheet. Prajeste for 30 - 35 mins pana se inmoaie and golden. Cool at room temperature.\n\nWhen just about cool whisk together all the dressing ingredients with a little more seasoning and gently toss through the potato chunks – use your hands to avoid breaking them up.', ru: 'Heat oven to 200C/180C fan/gas 6. Перемешайте the sweet potato chunks with the olive oil and some seasoning, and spread on a baking parchment-lined baking sheet. Запеките for 30 - 35 mins до мягкости and golden. Cool at room temperature.\n\nWhen just about cool whisk together all the dressing ingredients with a little more seasoning and gently toss through the potato chunks – use your hands to avoid breaking them up.', es: 'Heat oven to 200C/180C fan/gas 6. Mezcle the sweet potato chunks with the olive oil and some seasoning, and spread on a baking parchment-lined baking sheet. Ase for 30 - 35 mins hasta que este tierno and golden. Cool at room temperature.\n\nWhen just about cool whisk together all the dressing ingredients with a little more seasoning and gently toss through the potato chunks – use your hands to avoid breaking them up.' },
