    id: '53095',
    name: { en: 'Syrian Rice with Meat', ro: 'Orez sirian cu carne', ru: 'Сирийский рис с мясом', es: 'Arroz sirio con carne' },
    category: 'Miscellaneous',
    area: 'Syrian',
    instructions: { en: 'Heat 1/4 cup butter in a large saucepan over medium-high heat. Add ground beef and season with salt, allspice, cinnamon, and black pepper. Cook and stir until beef is browned and crumbly, 7 to 10 minutes.\n\nStir chicken broth and rice into beef in the saucepan; bring to a boil. Reduce heat to low, cover, and cook until liquid is absorbed, about 20 minutes.\n\nMeanwhile, melt 2 tablespoons butter in a small skillet over medium heat. Cook and stir pine nuts in hot butter until lightly browned, 3 to 5 minutes.\n\nMix pine nuts into beef-rice mixture before serving.', ro: 'Heat 1/4 cup butter in a large saucepan over medium-foc mare. Add ground beef and season with salt, allspice, cinnamon, and black pepper. Cook and amesteca pana cand beef is browned and crumbly, 7 to 10 minut.\n\nAmesteca chicken broth and rice into beef in the saucepan; adu la fierbere. Reduce heat to low, cover, and gateste pana cand liquid is absorbed, about 20 minut.\n\nMeanwhile, melt 2 tablespoons butter in a small skillet la foc mediu. Cook and stir pine nuts in hot butter until lightly browned, 3 to 5 minut.\n\nAmesteca pine nuts into beef-rice mixture before serving.', ru: 'Heat 1/4 cup butter in a large saucepan over medium-сильный огонь. Add ground beef and season with salt, allspice, cinnamon, and black pepper. Cook and перемешивайте пока beef is browned and crumbly, 7 to 10 минут.\n\nПеремешайте chicken broth and rice into beef in the saucepan; доведите до кипения. Reduce heat to low, cover, and готовьте до тех пор пока liquid is absorbed, about 20 минут.\n\nMeanwhile, melt 2 tablespoons butter in a small skillet на среднем огне. Cook and stir pine nuts in hot butter until lightly browned, 3 to 5 минут.\n\nСмешайте pine nuts into beef-rice mixture before serving.', es: 'Heat 1/4 cup butter in a large saucepan over medium-fuego alto. Add ground beef and season with salt, allspice, cinnamon, and black pepper. Cook and revuelva hasta que beef is browned and crumbly, 7 to 10 minutos.\n\nRevuelva chicken broth and rice into beef in the saucepan; lleve a ebullicion. Reduce heat to low, cover, and cocine hasta que liquid is absorbed, about 20 minutos.\n\nMeanwhile, melt 2 tablespoons butter in a small skillet a fuego medio. Cook and stir pine nuts in hot butter until lightly browned, 3 to 5 minutos.\n\nMezcle pine nuts into beef-rice mixture before serving.' },
