    id: '53093',
    name: { en: 'Syrian Spaghetti', ro: 'Spaghetti siriene', ru: 'Сирийские спагетти', es: 'Espagueti sirio' },
    category: 'Pasta',
    area: 'Syrian',
    instructions: { en: 'Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Grease a 9x13 inch baking dish.\n\nBring a large pot of lightly salted water to a boil. Add spaghetti and cook for 8 to 10 minutes or until al dente; drain and stir in tomato sauce, tomato paste, cinnamon, oil, salt and pepper. Transfer to prepared dish.\n\nBake in preheated oven for 1 hour, or until top is crunchy.', ro: 'Preincalzeste cuptorul la 350 grade F (175 grade C). Unge o 9x13 inch baking dish.\n\nBring a large pot of lightly salted water to a boil. Add spaghetti and gateste 8 to 10 minut or until al dente; drain and stir in tomato sauce, tomato paste, cinnamon, oil, salt and pepper. Transfera in prepared dish.\n\nCoace in preheated oven for 1 ora, or until top is crunchy.', ru: 'Разогрейте духовку до 350 градусов F (175 градусов C). Смажьте 9x13 inch baking dish.\n\nBring a large pot of lightly salted water to a boil. Add spaghetti and готовьте 8 to 10 минут or until al dente; drain and stir in tomato sauce, tomato paste, cinnamon, oil, salt and pepper. Переложите в prepared dish.\n\nВыпекайте in preheated oven for 1 час, or until top is crunchy.', es: 'Precaliente el horno a 350 grados F (175 grados C). Engrase una 9x13 inch baking dish.\n\nBring a large pot of lightly salted water to a boil. Add spaghetti and cocine 8 to 10 minutos or until al dente; drain and stir in tomato sauce, tomato paste, cinnamon, oil, salt and pepper. Transfiera a prepared dish.\n\nHornee in preheated oven for 1 hora, or until top is crunchy.' },
